Given the following job description, find and extract any mentions of salary or compensation.

Salary may be written in various formats, such as:

“$70,000 per year”, “INR 10 LPA”, “₹80,000/month”, “Competitive salary”, “Base pay range: $150,000 - $170,000/year”

If multiple mentions exist (e.g., base pay + bonuses), combine into one sentence.
If no salary is mentioned, return: “No salary information found.” The answer should be strictly brief and to the point. Only return pieces of information related to salary, ignore everything else.